WEBVTT

00:11:28.799 --> 00:11:30.180
because it kills your brand.

00:11:30.204 --> 00:11:32.260
And I said, you guys
have a trust business.

00:11:32.284 --> 00:11:35.095
And I spent three months --
three months --

00:11:35.119 --> 00:11:37.545
pleading with Dan to do the right thing.

00:11:37.569 --> 00:11:40.777
CA: So they could have said,
and in your view, should have said,

00:11:41.998 --> 00:11:44.498
"Alert, world, alert, American people.

00:11:44.522 --> 00:11:47.670
We've noticed that something terrible
has happened on our platform,

00:11:47.694 --> 00:11:51.549
a huge number of ads have gone out there
that frankly are not fact-based.

00:11:52.300 --> 00:11:54.522
Here are the steps
we're doing to shut it down.

00:11:54.546 --> 00:11:55.696
Meanwhile, beware."

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:58.426
That they could have said that
and should have said that.

00:11:58.450 --> 00:12:00.474
